    {
      "span": "来之不易",
      "translation": "hard-won",
      "tier": "phrase"
    },
    {
      "span": "别有洞天",
      "translation": "a world of its own",
      "tier": "phrase"
    },
    {
      "span": "还未等他反应过来",
      "translation": "before he could react",
      "tier": "sentence"
    },
    {
      "span": "筑基，成了。",
      "translation": "Foundation establishment — complete.",
      "tier": "sentence"
    },
    {
      "span": "剑光掠过山谷，像一道流星。",
      "translation": "The sword-light swept across the valley like a shooting star.",
      "tier": "sentence"
    },
    {
      "span": "沈长老盯着他看了很久，忽然笑了。",
      "translation": "Elder Shen stared at him for a long time — and then, suddenly, he smiled.",
      "tier": "sentence"
    },
    {
      "span": "天亮的时候，他已经能让灵气在体内走完一个小周天了。",
      "translation": "By dawn, he could already guide the spirit energy through a full lesser heavenly circuit.",
      "tier": "sentence"
    },
    {
      "span": "第一天，丹田胀得像要裂开。",
      "translation": "On the first day, his dantian swelled as if it were about to split open.",
      "tier": "sentence"
